# GitHub CLI Rules

## Default Settings
- Username: FritzMatthaeus
- Organization: hypeIT-GmbH

## Rules

### GitHub Issues
When handling GitHub issues:
- Use username: FritzMatthaeus
- Look for repositories in hypeIT-GmbH organization first
- If repository not found in hypeIT-GmbH, ask user for correct organization
- Default assignee: FritzMatthaeus

### GitHub Pull Requests
When handling GitHub pull requests:
- Use username: FritzMatthaeus
- Look for repositories in hypeIT-GmbH organization first
- If repository not found in hypeIT-GmbH, ask user for correct organization
- Default author: FritzMatthaeus

## Examples
```bash
# List open issues assigned to FritzMatthaeus
gh issue list -R hypeIT-GmbH/Producely-Go --assignee FritzMatthaeus --state open

# List open PRs by FritzMatthaeus
gh pr list -R hypeIT-GmbH/Producely-Go --author FritzMatthaeus --state open
```
